<p><a href="http://www.pokemonshowdown.com">Pokémon Showdown</a> is a Pok&eacute;mon battle simulator that you can play immediately in your browser with no downloads! <a href="http://www.pokemonshowdown.com">Try it out!</a></p>

<p>Smogon uses Pokémon Showdown for competitive battling, tournaments, and other community functions. For more information, visit the <a href="http://www.pokemonshowdown.com">Pokémon Showdown website</a> or the <a href="/forums/forumdisplay.php?f=209">forum</a>.</p>

